{"id": "sos010", "name": "Audio_ArcETC_695_12_11", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Alright, you got me. What's the deal?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "Just wanna chit chat, Sagar, that's all. You've been rather cocky recently.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee P"], "content": "Champion of the comprehensive physical ability test 3 times in a row? Breaking the record of long-distance running that's existed for 100 years? Knocking down 10 people in combat class? This is ridiculous, what's meds you on?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "How would I do that? They'd find it in the medical tests.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee L"], "content": "Already checked. You are an absolute beast, even your brain is full of muscles... Hehe, except your height is...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainees"], "content": "HAHAHAHAHA......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "You guys got me here just to mock me?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "No, we want to make a deal.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "A deal?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "You know as well as I do that they're just looking for the top guy. The higher-ups already noticed you early on. Ordinary people like us don't stand out easily.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee P"], "content": "Being trained like a dog every day, being forced to drop out of the team after a few years...... \nWe don't want that, so we wanna ask you for a favor. \n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "You want me to go easy on you guys during the exam?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee L"], "content": "Hey, hey, hey. That's not what I said. Isn't it nice to let others shine once in a while?\nIt's good for all of us.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I really respect the rules here, I think that there's a chance for everyone if you all work hard. Besides, mutual benefit? I am not hearing anything that's beneficial to me.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "Hey... if we cooperate, us three won't accidentally break your hand, does that count as a benefit?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps "], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Let me remind you guys, it's prohibited for trainees to fight in private...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "Oh, afraid? Aren't you the son of the illustrious Luka?\nShaming daddy like this......\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Just as expected, it's because of my dad... alright.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Objects Crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "If you wanna fight, I'm down!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "HA, HAHAHA, you're dead meat! Payne, Larry! Kick his a**!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Hmph!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch_Miss", "Fists "], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee P"], "content": "Holy s***, what the f***, he's a monster...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "Don't be scared! There are 3 of us! Surround him! \n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Blocks"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "...Ugh! Damn it...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Objects Crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainees"], "content": "!?!?!?!?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Enough, rookies... enough!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Officer... J-J-Jackal?</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "You know me, eh? This is my territory, why didn't you tell me this was going down?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee L"], "content": "O-Officer. we were just practicing......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "You call 3 fighting against 1 practicing? Bulls***.\nCome on now, let's do 1-on-1. You were the most eager to get started. You go first.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "T-This... if it's 1-on-1...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hurry up, how long do you want me to wait?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Trainee H"], "content": "D-Damn it! Sagar, you just wait and see!!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Ran away. F***ing babies. Ha, how many times have you been caught up in this type of s***? If I weren't on here to save your a**...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Mind your own business... I can handle them.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Duh, if you can't take down those trashy losers, I'd kill you myself.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... You wanna pick a fight? Now?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "You think I'm as dumb as those morons? Start a fight here? Look up.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......! Cameras?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Really depends if those old farts even care.\nListen closely, for next month's United Mission, our batch will be operating with the noobs... Let's end things then once and for all. Any questions?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Yeah. Can you leave me alone?\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hehe... once a Jackal's locked onto its prey, it won't let go easily... Hahaha!!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps "], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... F*** this...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……こんな所に呼び出して、何の用だ？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "ただお前と「お話」したいだけだよ、Sagar。\nお前最近調子に乗ってんじゃないか？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "実技の総合テストで3回連続優勝だって？\nなに？100年来の記録更新？\nんでもって、戦闘の授業では10人をぶっ飛ばした？\nありえねーだろ。なんか薬でもやってんじゃねーの？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "そんなわけないだろ。\nそんなことをすれば、身体検査で一発アウトだ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "とっくに調べたさ。\nお前は正真正銘の怪物だ。\n脳みそまで筋肉のな……はは、でもその身長は……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生たち"], "content": "くくっ……ははははは……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "俺を笑いものにするために呼び出したのか？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "いいや、取引しようぜ。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "取引？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "お前も知ってんだろ？\nここでは一番以外の人間は必要とされてない。\n上層部の奴らもとっくにお前には目を付けてると思うぜ。\nだけど、俺らみたいな一般人はそう簡単には行かないんだ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "毎日毎日死ぬほど苦しい思いをしながらしごかれて、最後には除隊を命じられる……そんなのはごめんだ。\nそこで、お前に頼みがある。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "テストで手を抜けってことか？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "そりゃ言い方が悪いぜ。\n仲間が順番に活躍できるんだぜ？\nお互いにいいとこ取りだ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "俺は、ここのルールに敬意を払ってる。\n努力すれば、皆にチャンスはあるはずだ。\nそれに、お互い良いところ取り？\n俺にメリットがあるようには感じなかったけど。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "そりゃあ……俺らに手を貸せば、腕を折られずに済むんだからな。\nメリットだろ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "言っておくけど、訓練生同士の私的な格闘は禁止されてるぞ……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "ビビってんのか？\nお前あの有名なLukaってやつの息子なんだろ？\nいいのか？そんな風に親父の顔に泥を塗るようなことしてさ……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……あぁ、父さんのことで俺を……わかった。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "やるなら来い！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "はっ！あははは！\nPayne、Larry！やってやれ！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はあ！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch_Miss", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "くそ！なんつー力だ……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "ビビるな！\nこっちは3人いるんだぞ！\n囲め！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "止める"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……ぐっ！くそ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生たち"], "content": "！？！？！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "はいはい、お前ら……そこまでだ！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">ジャっ……ジャ、ジャッカル……先輩？</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "あ？俺のこと知ってんのか？\n俺の縄張りでケンカすんのに、俺に断りも入れないってどういうことだよ？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "せ、先輩……俺らはただ練習してただけで……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "三人で一人をボコるのが練習だって？クソだな。\nおら、来いよ。\n一対一でやろうぜ。\nお前、さっきまで先頭きってたよな？\nじゃー、お前からだ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "いや、あの……一対一は……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "おら、早くしろよ。\nいつまで待たせる気だ？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "く……クソぉ！Sagar、覚えてろよ！！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "慌てた足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "あれ、逃げちった。\nお前虫けらにたかられるの何度目だ？\n今回は先輩様がそばにいたからよかったものの……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "余計なお世話だ……俺一人でもなんとかできた。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "んなこた分かってるっつーの。\nあんな虫けら3匹も倒せねぇようなやつ、俺が先にやってやるよ。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……お前もケンカ希望か？今ここで？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "俺をさっきの虫けらと同じにすんなよ。\n俺はそんなにバカじゃねぇ。\n上を見ろよ。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！ここ、監視カメラがあったのか。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "あとはおっさんたちが気に留めるか留めないかの差だな。\n来月の合同任務は、俺たちの代と新人で組む……そこで勝負を決めようぜ。\nなんか異論あるか？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ある。\n俺にちょっかい出すのはやめてくれ。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "へっへっへ……そりゃー無理な話だぜ。\nジャッカルは一度目を付けた獲物は逃がさないんだ……はっはっは！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……めんどくさ……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……把我找到這裡，有事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "只是想閒聊一下，Sagar。你最近很囂張呢。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "連續三次綜合體能測試冠軍？打破一百年來的長跑紀錄？還在搏擊課上打倒十個人？太誇張了，是不是用了什麼藥啊？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "怎麼可能？那種事查健檢紀錄就知道了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "早就查過了，你是貨真價實的怪物，連腦袋都長滿肌肉……嘿嘿，就是個子實在……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生們"], "content": "呵呵哈哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "你們是為了取笑我才約我來的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "不，只是想跟你做個交易。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "交易？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "你也知道，這裡只需要第一名的人才。上頭一定早就注意到你，我們這種普通人可就沒那麼容易了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "天天被操得要死要活，幾年後被勒令退隊……我們不想那樣，所以找你幫個忙。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "要我在測驗中放水？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "別說的這麼直。讓大夥輪流表現不是很好嗎？這可是互利啊。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我很尊敬這裡的規則，如果努力的話我覺得大家都有機會的。而且，互利？我聽不出我有什麼好處。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "嘿……合作的話，就可以避免被我們三個折斷一隻手，這算不算好處？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我提醒你們，訓練生禁止私鬥……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "怕了嗎？你不是那個赫赫有名的 Luka 的兒子？這樣丟老爸的臉……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……果然是因為我爸……好吧。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "想打的話，我奉陪！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "哈、哈哈哈，找死！Payne、Larry！給我上！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哼！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch_Miss", "揮拳"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "○的，這什麼力氣……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "別怕！我們可是有三個人！把他圍起來！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "格擋"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……唔！可惡……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生們"], "content": "！？！？！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "好了，菜鳥……到此為止！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">豺、豺、豺狼……學長？</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "認得我啊？那在我的地盤裡幹架，怎麼不通知一聲啊？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "學、學長，我們只是在練習而已……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "三個打一個叫練習？狗屎。\n來來來，一對一決鬥，你剛剛跑最前面吧？從你開始。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "這、這個……一對一的話……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "快啊，是要讓我等多久？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "可……可惡！Sagar，給我記著！！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "逃掉了。哈，這是你第幾次被蟲子給纏上啦？要不是我這個學長剛好在場……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "多管閒事……我自己就能解決他們。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "廢話，如果你連那種三流貨色也幹不掉，我他○的就先幹掉你。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……你也想打？現在？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "當我跟那三個一樣蠢？在這裡開打？看上面。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！原來這裡有監視器？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "差別在於那些老屁股想不想管而已。\n你聽著，下個月的聯合任務，我們這梯會和菜鳥一起行動……咱們就在那時做個了斷。有沒有意見？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "有。你能不能別來煩我？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘿嘿……豺狼一旦盯上獵物，是不會鬆口的……哈哈哈！！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……真是麻煩啊……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......여기로 날 불러 내다니, 무슨 용건이지?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "그냥 같이 얘기 좀 하고 싶어서, Sagar.\n최근에 엄청 미쳐 날뛰던데?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 P"], "content": "3연속 실기 테스트 1등? 백 년 만에 신기록 갱신? 호신술 수업에서 10명을 상대? 이건 말도 안 된다고. 무슨 약물이라도 주입한 거 아니야?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "약물은 무슨. \n그런 건 건강 검진 기록을 보면 다 알 거 아니야?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 L"], "content": "물론 다 찾아봤지. \n진짜 역대급 괴물이더군.\n뇌까지 아주 근육으로 무장했던데....하하하, 그런 녀석이....\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생들"], "content": "크흡....하하하하하......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "날 비웃고 싶어서 이렇게 불러낸 거야?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "아니, 그냥 간단한 거래 좀 하고 싶어서.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "거래?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "너도 알겠지만, 이곳에선 오직 1등 이외에는 모두 들러리가 될 뿐이야. 윗선에서도 분명 널 주시하고 있겠지. 우리 같은 일반인들에겐 확실히 꿈같은 얘기야.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 P"], "content": "매일 죽기 살기로 살아가다가 몇 년 뒤엔 강제 퇴역 선고를 받게 되겠지... 우린 그런 거 원하지 않아. 그래서 이렇게 네게 부탁을 하고 싶은 거야.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "테스트에서 봐달라는 얘기인가?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 L"], "content": "너무 그런 식으로 말하지는 말아 줬으면 하는데?\n동료들끼리 서로 돌아가면서 활약하는 것도 나쁘진 않잖아? 서로에게 이득이 될 거라고 생각하는데?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "난 이곳의 규율에 큰 경외심을 가지고 있어. 만약 너희들도 열심히 노력한다면, 분명 해낼 수 있을 거라고 생각해. 그리고, 서로에게 이득이라고? 난 내게 있어서 어떤 이득이 있는지 잘 모르겠는데?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "......우리에게 협력하겠다면, 우리 셋이 네 녀석의 팔 하나를 부러뜨리는 것쯤은 면할 수 있으니까, 좋은 거 아닐까?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "말해두는데, 훈련생들끼리 사적인 싸움은 금지되어 있...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "쫄은 건가? 네가 그 유명한 Luka의 아들이라며? 이런 식으로 아버지의 얼굴에 먹칠을 할 셈이냐...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......역시 아버지 때문에 그런 거였군. 좋다.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "어디 덤벼보라고!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "하! 하하하하! \nPayne, Larry! 박살을 내주자고!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "이얏!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch_Miss", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 P"], "content": "제길, 어떻게 이런 힘이...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "겁먹지 마! 우린 세 명이라고! 저 녀석을 포위하자!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "막아선다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": ".....큭, 제길......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생들"], "content": "!?!?!?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "좋아, 좋아~ 햇병아리들....여기까지!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">우, 우, 우, 울프... 선배?</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "음? 날 알아? 내 구역에서 쌈박질할 거면, 미리 언지라도 줬으면 좋았잖아?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 L"], "content": "서, 선배... 저희는 그냥 연습의 일환으로...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "세 명이서 한 명 다굴까는 연습? \n개소리를 아주 잘도 늘어놓는구나.\n자자, 1 대 1 결투로 가자고. 방금 네가 가장 앞에 서있었지? 좋아, 너부터 시작하자.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "저, 그게... 1대1은....\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "빨리 안 해? 언제까지 기다리게 할 거야?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["훈련생 H"], "content": "제......제길! Sagar, 두고 보자!!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "도망가 버렸군. 하, 네 녀석 대체 몇 번이나 저런 식으로 골머리를 썩어야겠냐? 마침 이 선배님이 곁에 있어서 망정이지...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "괜한 참견했군... 나 혼자서도 저 녀석들 정도는 충분했다고.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "그걸 말이라고. 네 녀석이 저런 떨거지 3명한테 나가떨어졌다면, 나도 바로 네 녀석부터 작살을 냈을 거다.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......너도 싸우자고? 지금?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "지금 나를 저 떨거지들과 똑같이 취급하는 거냐? 여기서 싸운다니? 위를 보라고?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......! 가, 감시 카메라!?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "늙은 너구리들이 저런 걸 일일이 확인할지 안 할지는 모르겠지만.\n잘 들어라. 다음 달에 연합 임무에서, 우리들은 신입들과 함께 임무를 수행하게 된다...결판은 그때 내자고. 이견 있어?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "있어. \n제발 날 좀 그만 따라다녀 줬으면 하는데.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "크크큭.....원래 울프는 사냥감을 한 번 물면 절대 놓지 않거든....크하하하하!!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......성가셔 죽겠군....\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……把我找到這裡，有事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "只是想閒聊一下，Sagar。你最近很囂張呢。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "連續三次綜合體能測試冠軍？打破一百年來的長跑紀錄？還在搏擊課上打倒十個人？太誇張了，是不是用了什麼藥啊？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "怎麼可能？那種事查健檢紀錄就知道了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "早就查過了，你是貨真價實的怪物，連腦袋都長滿肌肉……嘿嘿，就是個子實在……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生們"], "content": "呵呵哈哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "你們是為了取笑我才約我來的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "不，只是想跟你做個交易。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "交易？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "你也知道，這裡只需要第一名的人才。上頭一定早就注意到你，我們這種普通人可就沒那麼容易了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "天天被操得要死要活，幾年後被勒令退隊……我們不想那樣，所以找你幫個忙。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "要我在測驗中放水？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "別說的這麼直。讓大夥輪流表現不是很好嗎？這可是互利啊。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我很尊敬這裡的規則，如果努力的話我覺得大家都有機會的。而且，互利？我聽不出我有什麼好處。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "嘿……合作的話，就可以避免被我們三個折斷一隻手，這算不算好處？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "我提醒你們，訓練生禁止私鬥……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "怕了嗎？你不是那個赫赫有名的 Luka 的兒子？這樣丟老爸的臉……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……果然是因為我爸……好吧。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "想打的話，我奉陪！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "哈、哈哈哈，找死！Payne、Larry！給我上！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哼！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch_Miss", "揮拳"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 P"], "content": "○的，這什麼力氣……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "別怕！我們可是有三個人！把他圍起來！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "格擋"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……唔！可惡……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生們"], "content": "！？！？！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "好了，菜鳥……到此為止！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">豺、豺、豺狼……學長？</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "認得我啊？那在我的地盤裡幹架，怎麼不通知一聲啊？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 L"], "content": "學、學長，我們只是在練習而已……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "三個打一個叫練習？狗屎。\n來來來，一對一決鬥，你剛剛跑最前面吧？從你開始。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "這、這個……一對一的話……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "快啊，是要讓我等多久？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["訓練生 H"], "content": "可……可惡！Sagar，給我記著！！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "逃掉了。哈，這是你第幾次被蟲子給纏上啦？要不是我這個學長剛好在場……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "多管閒事……我自己就能解決他們。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "廢話，如果你連那種三流貨色也幹不掉，我他○的就先幹掉你。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……你也想打？現在？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "當我跟那三個一樣蠢？在這裡開打？看上面。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！原來這裡有監視器？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "差別在於那些老屁股想不想管而已。\n你聽著，下個月的聯合任務，我們這梯會和菜鳥一起行動……咱們就在那時做個了斷。有沒有意見？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "有。你能不能別來煩我？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘿嘿……豺狼一旦盯上獵物，是不會鬆口的……哈哈哈！！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……真是麻煩啊……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……把我找到这里，有事吗？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["训练生 H"], "content":